thread.title: Dutch art dealer discovers first 'new' Rembrandt in 44 years

title: Dutch art dealer discovers first 'new' Rembrandt in 44 years
text:
Dutch art dealer discovers first 'new' Rembrandt in 44 years 10:51pm IST - 00:46
The first 'new' Rembrandt since 1974 is put on display at the Hermitage museum in Amsterdam after being discovered by a Dutch art dealer at an auction house in 2016. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
